group of lvl 51 wizards.  Most dk blue mobs at that level have no more than 10khp.  6 wizards opening with Ice Comet = 6720 right away.  If pulled with snare, then wizard with aggro could kite, while the other 5 launch another round of IC = Dead Mob.<br>
