I think sometimes we underestimate ourselves when it comes to grouping.  Now this couldn't work in places like PoP, when the mobs have much higher hp's, and hit harder.  Situational, maybe.  Fun, you betcha.<br>
<br>
We were in PoN last night, and the difference in my group when the Mage left, and was replaced by a druid was dramatic.  The fights lasted much longer, the cleric used much more mana....  <br>
